data.description: New Roof!. Save money and time! Inspections have been completed and are available to view. MOTIVATED SELLERS! This one is ready to Go! Discover an exceptional opportunity with this exceptional Lake Front First Tier Home! This Ranch-style gem comes complete with a rare private double-decker dock, gentle slope to the water, large lot, catering to both leisure and water enthusiasts. Step inside to find a thoughtfully designed layout that maximizes the captivating waterfront setting. This home is equipped with a whole home generator! The master bedroom on the main level features a sliding door leading to a deck with sweeping lake views, ensuring a serene start and end to your day. Four bedrooms on the main level offer comfort and privacy, while the lower level presents a finished walk-out basement with a second full kitchen, two additional bedrooms perfect for lakeside gatherings. Nestled within the award-winning Lee's Summit School District. However, the true allure lies in the myriad recreational opportunities Lake Winnebago offers – from boating, water skiing, and fishing to dining at the Arrowhead Yacht Club Community Restaurant. Outdoor enthusiasts will relish hiking trails, tennis courts, pickleball, basketball, equestrian facilities and more. More than a home, this Lake Front First Tier Home presents a lifestyle, an invitation to embrace vacation-inspired living every day. It's a rare chance to invest in experiences, surrounded by the beauty of nature. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Lake Winnebago oasis your own.
